Package: empCop
Type: Package
Title: Classes and tools for some empirical or semi-parametrical models for copulas.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Oskar Laverny
Maintainer: Oskar Laverny <oskar.laverny@gmail.com>
Description: This package notably gives (for the moment) tools to work with Empirical 
  checkerboard copula, empirical checkerboard copula with known margins and convex 
  combinaisons of copulas. It uses the main classes and formal generics from the 
  `copula` package.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
